text:
[redacted_address] sold at auction over the weekend for $1,558,000! An amazing $200,000 over the reserve and a fantastic result for the vendors!
If there is anything I can do to assist you with your property needs, whether you're looking to buy or sell or have questions about the current market, please don't hesitate to contact me anytime. I am more than happy to help.
Have a great week!
[redacted_name]
P&G Real Estate
